wiki.summary: “she’s all i wanna be” is a song written and recorded by Tate McRae for her debut album "i used to think i could fly", released on May 27, 2022. The song started to get traction when a snippet was posted on TikTok. Later, the track began being teased in multiple videos posted by McRae. According to her, the song began as a ballet to show how sad the story of the relationship was to her. She began changing it to the upbeat pop song that was released to attract more listeners. Read more on Last.fm.
wiki.content: “she’s all i wanna be” is a song written and recorded by Tate McRae for her debut album "i used to think i could fly", released on May 27, 2022. The song started to get traction when a snippet was posted on TikTok. Later, the track began being teased in multiple videos posted by McRae. According to her, the song began as a ballet to show how sad the story of the relationship was to her. She began changing it to the upbeat pop song that was released to attract more listeners. “she’s all i wanna be” debuted at #52 on the Billboard Hot 100, during the week of February 19, 2022.
